# This directory is populated at runtime by publish.py and propose.py:
#
#   performance-log.md   — one line per skill published, for outcome tracking
#   pr-bodies.md         — pre-written awesome-list PR bodies from last publish
#   evolution-log.md     — audit trail of capability-layer changes over time
#
# These files are gitignored except for this .gitkeep, so the directory exists
# but stays empty on fresh clones.
